Sentencas: The development of high-performance cathodes is crucial for intermediate temperature SOFCs.
Titulo: In-situ self-assembly nano-fibrous perovskite cathode excluding Sr and Co with superior performance for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Thereinto, morphology regulation is an effective way to improve the electrocatalytic activity of SOFC cathodes.
Titulo: In-situ self-assembly nano-fibrous perovskite cathode excluding Sr and Co with superior performance for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Nanofibers have been confirmed with the advantages of large specific surface area and high porosity over traditional nanoparticles, possessing a significant promotion effect on oxygen reduction reaction (ORR) activity.
Titulo: In-situ self-assembly nano-fibrous perovskite cathode excluding Sr and Co with superior performance for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: However, the traditional cell fabrication with high-temperature sintering will break the fiber structure and cause agglomeration.
Titulo: In-situ self-assembly nano-fibrous perovskite cathode excluding Sr and Co with superior performance for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Herein, we adopted a sintering-free method to in-situ self-assemble La0.6Ca0.4Fe0.8Ni0.2O3-delta (LCaFN) nanofibers onto the YSZ electrolyte surface by polarization operation, which showed impressive performance compared to our previous work.
Titulo: In-situ self-assembly nano-fibrous perovskite cathode excluding Sr and Co with superior performance for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: After polarization for 21 h, the peak power density of the cell at 700 degrees C increased from 0.36 W center dot cm-2 to 0.60 W center dot cm-2, and the highest peak power density at 750 degrees C could approach 0.91 W center dot cm-2.
Titulo: In-situ self-assembly nano-fibrous perovskite cathode excluding Sr and Co with superior performance for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Meanwhile, the cell showed good long-term durability with a current density of about 0.35 A center dot cm-2 at 0.7 V and 650 degrees C for 90 h. This work manifests that the combi-nation of fiber cathodes and in-situ self-assembly techniques is a promising strategy for high-performance SOFCs.(c) 2023
Titulo: In-situ self-assembly nano-fibrous perovskite cathode excluding Sr and Co with superior performance for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
